124
00:17:13.999 --> 00:17:16.751
- Ei!
- Cuidado!


125
00:17:18.962 --> 00:17:20.880
Estou entrando, tio Ned.

126
00:17:48.658 --> 00:17:52.912
Estou chegando,
tia CIara, tia Martha.


127
00:17:53.705 --> 00:17:55.831
